---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

import ContactCTA from "../components/ContactCTA.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Ryan Acevedo" description="About Ryan Acevedo">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="I'm an engineer by training and a problem-solver by nature."
			>
				<Image
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/ryan-acevedo-beanie.jpeg"
					alt="Ryan Acevedo on an air balloon smile with a beanie on"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<!-- Story sections -->
			<section class="story-block">
				<div class="story-accent"></div>
				<div class="story-content">
					<p>
						I spent my career building software systems, debugging
						complex architectures, and figuring out how things work
						from the inside out. But the biggest problem I've ever
						tackled isn't technical&nbsp;&mdash; it's building a
						business from scratch that proves convenience and
						compassion aren't mutually exclusive.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="story-block highlight">
				<h2 class="callout-title">The Problem</h2>
				<div class="story-content">
					<p>
						I grew up watching people in my community getting chewed
						up by the system. As someone who was formerly
						incarcerated, I experienced firsthand the barriers that
						most people never think about: can't get hired, can't
						get housing, can't get a fresh start no matter how hard
						they work.
					</p>
					<p class="punch">That never sat right with me.</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="story-block">
				<h2 class="callout-title">The Mission</h2>
				<div class="story-content">
					<p>
						So when I started my first business <a
							href="https://mobileoilhero.com">Mobile Oil Hero</a
						>, I didn't just want to build another service business.
						I wanted to build a company where the mission is baked
						into the operating model. Every oil change we perform
						funds real jobs for people who've earned a shot. Every
						customer who books with us is choosing to put their
						money where their values are.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="story-block">
				<div class="story-content">
					<p>
						The truth is, I'm a first-time founder figuring this out
						as I go. But that's the engineer in me&nbsp;&mdash;
						break it down, solve one piece at a time, and don't stop
						until it works.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="story-block highlight closing">
				<div class="story-content">
					<p>
						I have a proven track record of building successful
						businesses. But this time, I'm doing it for a different
						reason. This time it's.. it's to change the system.
					</p>
					<p class="punch">
						That's my story. Now it's time for change.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<ContactCTA message="Ready to make an impact?" />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
		max-width: 52rem;
		margin-inline: auto;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	/* Story blocks */
	.story-block {
		position: relative;
		padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
		font-size: var(--text-base);
		line-height: 1.75;
		border-left: 3px solid transparent;
	}

	.story-block .story-accent {
		position: absolute;
		left: -3px;
		top: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		width: 3px;
		background: var(--gradient-accent);
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	.story-block .story-content {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	/* Highlighted story blocks */
	.story-block.highlight {
		background: rgba(118, 17, 166, 0.08);
		border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-regular);
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	.callout-title {
		font-family: var(--font-brand);
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.callout-title::after {
		content: "";
		display: block;
		width: 2rem;
		height: 3px;
		background: var(--gradient-accent);
		border-radius: 2px;
		margin-top: 0.4rem;
	}

	/* Punch lines */
	.punch {
		font-family: var(--font-brand);
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--gray-0);
		margin-top: 0.25rem;
	}

	.closing .punch {
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		background: var(--gradient-accent);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	/* Skills */
	.skills-section {
		padding: 1.5rem 0;
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0.75rem 0 0 0;
	}

	.skills li {
		padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: var(--accent-regular);
		color: var(--accent-text-over);
		font-family: var(--font-brand);
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			gap: 2.5rem;
		}

		.story-block {
			padding: 2rem 2.5rem 2rem 2.5rem;
			font-size: var(--text-md);
		}

		.story-block.highlight {
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.callout-title {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}

		.punch {
			font-size: var(--text-xl);
		}

		.closing .punch {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}

		.skills li {
			font-size: var(--text-sm);
			padding: 0.625rem 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
